        <para id="id26379622">What kind of energy does the moving tennis ball have?</para>
        <para id="id25680502">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id25680508">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id26378269">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id25667465">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id25679694">______________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id26367244">This has probably made you suspect that energy can be changed. When there is a change in energy from one kind to another kind, we speak of the conversion of energy.</para>
